{"tid":1906073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"憂鬱後遺症","createTime":"2020-03-01T16:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T20:28:50.000Z","uid":194166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a16cd9b49b49d490e7408ed0541bf0f95fb66478","tid":1906073,"uid":194166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"有沒人有過憂鬱症之後，分析力高左好多，睇野睇到本質。<br />\n<br />\n身邊人話自己好成熟理性 ，但是其實好頹，畢竟有好多野個事實係負面，個人會好痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n除左買股票左之外，好似清醒過人並沒咩用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d104ef32d7711c6b4b15ea5a717a2ae39de2a6","tid":1906073,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"舉下例 睇到咩本質？"},{"pid":"fba6e670ffd5bdb4068b2ebf7e370e5b984368e6","tid":1906073,"uid":194166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d104ef32d7711c6b4b15ea5a717a2ae39de2a6","tid":1906073,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"舉下例 睇到咩本質？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"有沒留意學校同社會唔會教你點理財同投資，只會叫你好好地讀書，搵錢，消費。因為資本家就係要源源不盡嘅高級打工仔，set好一個框框，就有無盡嘅廉價勞動力。"},{"pid":"114f4efe91f1ae70784e8163fa88cd19e35b4600","tid":1906073,"uid":194166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d104ef32d7711c6b4b15ea5a717a2ae39de2a6","tid":1906073,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"舉下例 睇到咩本質？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"發覺好難舉例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddb8ea80f41cb695f6098987597be88669440da","tid":1906073,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"有抑鬱症<br />\n冇憂鬱症"},{"pid":"31afc3a5f6bd60b4745254c67e1e137b3a8c9158","tid":1906073,"uid":315798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"通常有情緒病嘅人都係會比較抽離去睇呢個世界"},{"pid":"c4f55e73bf26803e84c7d6cd0cb692e10186fb8f","tid":1906073,"uid":57566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:28:50.000Z","msg":"用理性去解答所有問題<br />\n其實只係唔想面對自己既感性<br />\n分離自己既情緒令自己唔去感覺<br />\n當我意識到依樣野既時候<br />\n我發現我真係好病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}